Class SourceInfoCloner

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.waters.model.base.DefaultProxyVisitor

        • net.sourceforge.waters.model.module.ModuleProxyCloner
          • net.sourceforge.waters.model.compiler.context.SourceInfoCloner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProxyCloner, ProxyVisitor, ModuleProxyVisitor

    public class SourceInfoCloner
extends ModuleProxyCloner
    An implementation of a ModuleProxyCloner that tracks source information while cloning. Every time a Proxy is duplicated by this cloner, a reference from the copy to the original is filed in the cloner's CompilationInfo.
    Author:
    Robi Malik
